WEBVTT

00:02:30.768 --> 00:02:34.064
And human speech is very complex.

00:02:34.088 --> 00:02:36.784
Take this sentence for instance.

00:02:37.088 --> 00:02:40.344
This sentence seems simple, 
but it's far from it.

00:02:40.368 --> 00:02:43.778
Now I will say this sentence 
in three different ways,

00:02:43.778 --> 00:02:45.898
and the meaning will change.

00:02:46.048 --> 00:02:50.584
"We" are eager to serve you.
So here we have stressed on "we."

00:02:50.608 --> 00:02:55.424
We are eager to serve "you,"
Here "you" has been given importance.

00:02:55.448 --> 00:02:59.784
We are "eager" to serve you,
here we have stressed on "eager."

00:02:59.808 --> 00:03:02.824
By stressing on three different words,